original: Karlström, Gustaf Fredrik Vilhelm Henry, tandläkare, Jönköping, f. 13/ 6/97 i Jönköp. av J. W. Karlström o. Emma Johansson. G. 29 m. Iris Wei-mer. Barn: Gösta f. 30, Bertil 34. — Stud :ex. i Lund 19, tandl :kand. 24, tandläk. 26. Praktik i Jönköp. sed. 26.
translated: Karlström, Gustaf Fredrik Vilhelm Henry, dentist, Jönköping, b. 13/6/97 in Jönköping, son of J.W. Karlström and Emma Johansson. Married on 29 [date missing] to Iris Wei-mer. Children: Gösta b. 30, Bertil b. 34. Studied examination in Lund in 19, dental candidate in 24, dentist in 26. Practiced in Jönköping since 26.
